'''Enigmatic Page (XI)''' is a Quest Item obtained from an investigation point in [[The Narzissenkreuz Ordo]]. It can be deciphered at [[Canotila and the Book of Revealing]].

==Location==
<gallery>
Item Enigmatic Page (XI) Location.png|Location
Item Enigmatic Page (XI) Location Context.png|Additional Context 
</gallery>

==Text==
...Shall be the passage between the primordial and the present...<br>
...Deconstruct and reverse its utility, and internalize...<br>
...Use to fully master...

...Matrimony of chemistry, bonding of the elements...<br>
...Circular ruins, forest in the mirror...

...Send [[Lyris]] and [[Jakob]] to...

(Most of the content has dissolved, and is beyond comprehension.)

==Trivia==
* "Matrimony of chemistry," "Circular ruins," and "forest in the mirror" are likely references to the real-world novels ''{{w|Chemical Wedding of Christian Rosenkreutz}}'', ''{{w|The Circular Ruins}}'' and ''{{w|Alice's Adventures in Wonderland}}'', respectively.
